"Looking for a bag that’s fluffy and shiny as a gold mine? Look no further than our Cloud Bag with a golden chain! This ultimately decent bag is made with the softest and highest-quality vegan leather, so carrying it around feels the lightest and comfiest. 
And it comes with a golden link chain embellishment that goes nicely on your shoulder to give a luxurious touch to this bag. Not just this but this bag has a detachable shoulder strap, so you can carry it like a sling if you want. 
This bag is just the right size for carrying all your everyday essentials, like your phone, lipstick, and wallet. So why settle for a boring bag when you can have this decent and stylish bag from Chokore? "

Design: This bag features a cloud design with a golden link chain handle that adds a touch of elegance to your outfit.

Material: Made with high-quality Vegan leather, this bag is durable, sturdy, and designed to last. 

Capacity:With a large capacity, this handbag has ample space for carrying all your essentials like your mobile, keys, makeup, wallet, and much more.

Versatility:This bag is suitable for a wide range of occasions, including work, shopping, travel, and everyday use. Also, it comes with a long strap, allowing you to carry it as a sling or cross-body bag as well.

Size: 28*6*36 cm (size includes the handle as well).

Title: Chokore Rectangle Retro Sunglasses with UV Protection (Mauve)
Description:
"Introducing our latest fashion obsession: rectangle retro sunglasses! These bad boys are the perfect accessory for anyone who wants to rock a vintage look with a modern twist.
Not only do these sunglasses provide the ultimate eye protection from harmful UV rays, but they also add an extra dose of coolness to any outfit. Plus, their rectangular shape is sure to flatter any face shape and give you that effortlessly chic vibe. Made with the highest quality materials, these shades are built to last through all your adventures - whether you're hitting up a music festival, lounging on the beach, or just strutting your stuff down the street. So go ahead, channel your inner 70s style icon with these rectangle retro sunglasses. You'll be turning heads and making a statement wherever you go!"
Details:
Superior UV Protection: These sunglasses offer exceptional UV protection with their UV 400 protection, shielding your eyes from harmful UVA and UVB rays and ensuring optimal eye health.

Trendy & Versatile Design: These sunglasses feature a trendy rectangular style and catchy hue that complements every face shape and will cater to your unique taste.

Enhanced visual comfort: These sunglasses feature polarized lenses that reduce glare from reflective surfaces, such as water, snow, or roads. This technology enhances visual comfort, minimizes eye strain, and improves overall visibility.

Complete Protection Package: These sunglasses come with a protective case and a microfiber cleaning cloth, ensuring that your sunglasses stay safe and clean while on the go.

Premium Lens Quality: Crafted with precision, these sunglasses feature high-quality lenses that provide crystal-clear vision without distortions. The lenses are made with acrylic with a frame made of polycarbonate, which ensures durability and long-lasting performance.

Size:14.5 cm length and 4.5 cm height
MRP is inclusive of all taxes.
